[Unlike most if the outbreaks that have been posted on ProMED, it seems that much of the pertussis burden in Ontario, Canada has been occurring in a religious cohort in the province that had not been immunized. - Mod.LL

Ontario, Canada, can be located using the HealthMap/ProMEDmail interactive map at:
